#: wp-admin/includes/class-wp-site-health.php:1925
msgid "Your site may have problems auto-updating plugins and themes"
msgstr "Maaaring magkaroon ng problema ang iyong site sa pag-auto-update ng mga plugin at tema"

#: wp-admin/includes/class-wp-site-health.php:1906
msgid "Plugin and theme auto-updates appear to be configured correctly"
msgstr "Mukhang maayos na naka-configure ang mga auto-update ng plugin at tema"

#: wp-admin/includes/class-wp-site-health.php:1872
